      "You agree not to: (a) use the Website in any way that violates any applicable federal, state, local, or international law; (b) attempt to interfere with or disrupt the Website or servers; (c) use any robot, spider, or other automatic device to access the Website; (d) introduce any viruses, trojan horses, or other material that is malicious or harmful.",
      "You are responsible for verifying any calculations or information with qualified professionals before making important decisions.",
    ],
  },
  {
